      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ファラ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Farah</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>リッド</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Reid</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>このあたりに
マリントルーパーの
セネルっていう人がいるらしいよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Apparently there's a marine trooper
in this area named Senel around here.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>その人に頼んで
漁師の仕事紹介してもらおうよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We should see if we can ask him
if he can get us jobs as fishmen.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いやいや、待てよ。
漁師になるんだったら
猟師のままでべつにいいじゃねぇか</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No, no, wait. If you're gonna go be a fisherman,
isn't it perfectly fine to just stay a hunter like you
already are?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>大丈夫！　イケる、イケる！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's all good! No problem, no problem!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>7</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ごまかすな！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't evade the question!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>6</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
